  "title": "Maintenance Operation",
  "description": "<ul><li>Preventive Maintenance Implementation: Performed scheduled preventive and corrective maintenance on critical industrial machines to improve reliability and reduce unexpected breakdowns</li></ul><ul><li>Safety & Compliance Execution: Performed all tasks following strict company SOPs and safety standards,</li></ul><ul><li>maintaining a safe and compliant working environment.</li></ul><ul><li>Hands-On Troubleshooting: Interpreted electrical schematics, dismantled and reassembled machines, and</li><li>resolved electrical and mechanical faults effectively.</li></ul><ul><li>Preventive Maintenance Scheduling: Created, verified, and executed preventive maintenance schedules to reduce downtime and extend machine lifespan across multiple production lines.</li><li>Electrical Troubleshooting: Diagnosed and repaired complex electrical and electronic faults in machinery to ensure continuous and reliable operations.</li><li>Team Reporting & Support: Assisted Maintenance Manager with accurate monthly and annual reporting while mentoring junior technicians in practical fault diagnosis..</li></ul>",
